<td class="persondata-label">NAME</td>
<td>Madoff, Bernard L.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="persondata-label">ALTERNATIVE NAMES</td>
<td>Bernie Madoff</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="persondata-label">SHORT DESCRIPTION</td>
<td>The former <a href="/wiki/Chairman" title="Chairman">chairman</a> of <a href="/wiki/NASDAQ" title="NASDAQ">NASDAQ</a>, he plead guilty to perpetrating <a href="/wiki/Securities_fraud" title="Securities fraud">securities fraud</a>.</td>
</tr>
